<td><code v-pre>Flux.just(1,2).map(i -&gt; i*2)</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>flatMap</strong></td>
<td>异步转换（返回Publisher）</td>
<td><code v-pre>Flux.just(1,2).flatMap(i -&gt; Mono.just(i*2))</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>zip</strong></td>
<td>合并多个流（按元素顺序配对）</td>
<td><code v-pre>Mono.zip(monoA, monoB, (a,b) -&gt; a + b)</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>merge</strong></td>
<td>合并多个流（按元素到达顺序）</td>
<td><code v-pre>Flux.merge(fluxA, fluxB)</code></td>
</tr>
